Teambaduk Hackathon App

Idea: A centralized app to cut down on paperwork and time taken for business decisions. 

Implementation: Using android studio/IntelliJ to create the application, MariaDB/MySQL to handle database.

Features to implement:
1. Proper layout for document viewing.
2. Implement upload function.
3. Implement signing of documents.
4. Fix login authorization.
5. Set up hierarchy tree for authorization to view and sign documents. (Database)
6. Improve upon the design and layout of overall app.


